[section#exec.run.loop.members
    [:en] Member functions
    [:zh_CN] 成员函数
]

[codeblock:declaration]
[[redoc("*>")]]run-loop-opstate-base* [[redoc("*>")]]pop-front();
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Blocks ([#defns.block]) until one of the following conditions is [`true]:
[:zh_CN] 阻塞（[#defns.block]）直至以下条件之一为 [`true]：
[list]
[item]
[:en] The [`run_loop] instance[=']s count is 0 and its state is finishing,
in which case [*pop-front] sets the state to finished and returns [`nullptr]; or
[:zh_CN] 该 [`run_loop] 实例的计数为 0 且其状态为“终止中”，这种情况下 [*pop-front]
将状态设为“已终止”并返回 [`nullptr]；或者
[item]
[:en] The [`run_loop] instance[=']s count is greater than 0, in which case an
item is removed from the front of the queue, the count is decremented by [`1],
and the removed item is returned.
[:zh_CN] 该 [`run_loop] 实例的计数大于 [`0]，这种情况下从队列前端移除一项，
计数减少 [`1]，并返回所移除项。
[list:end]
[div:end]

[codeblock:declaration]
void [[redoc("*>")]]push-back([[redoc("*>")]]run-loop-opstate-base* item);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Adds [`item] to the back of the queue and increments the [`run_loop]
instance[=']s count by 1.
[:zh_CN] 向队列后端添加 [`item] 并使该 [`run_loop] 实例的计数增加 [`1]。

[para:sync]
[:en] This operation synchronizes with the [*pop-front] operation that obtains [`item].
[:zh_CN] 此操作同步于获取了 [`item] 的 [*pop-front] 操作。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member get_scheduler[!run_loop]]
[codeblock:declaration]
[[redoc("*>")]]run-loop-scheduler get_scheduler();
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:returns]
[:en] An instance of [*run-loop-scheduler]
that can be used to schedule work onto this [`run_loop] instance.
[:zh_CN] 一个 [*run-loop-scheduler] 实例，可用于向此 [`run_loop] 实例调度工作。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member run[!run_loop]]
[codeblock:declaration]
void run();
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:expects]
[:en] The [`run_loop] instance[=']s state is either starting or finishing.
[:zh_CN] 此 [`run_loop] 实例的状态为“启动中”或“终止中”。

[para:effects]
[:en] If the [`run_loop] instance[=']s state is starting, sets the state to running,
otherwise leaves the state unchanged.
[:zh_CN] 如果此 [`run_loop] 实例的状态为“启动中”，则将其状态设值为“运行中”，
否则保留其状态不变。

[:en] Then, equivalent to:
[:zh_CN] 然后，等价于：
[codeblock]
while (auto* op = [[redoc("*>")]]pop-front()) {
  op->[[redoc("*>")]]execute();
}
[codeblock:end]

[para:remarks]
[:en] When the [`run_loop] instance[=']s state changes, it does so without introducing data races.
[:zh_CN] 当此 [`run_loop] 实例的状态改变时，不会引入数据竞争。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member finish[!run_loop]]
[codeblock:declaration]
void finish();
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:expects]
[:en] The [`run_loop] instance[=']s state is either starting or running.
[:zh_CN] 此 [`run_loop] 实例的状态为“启动中”或“运行中”。

[para:effects]
[:en] Changes the [`run_loop] instance[=']s state to finishing.
[:zh_CN] 将此 [`run_loop] 实例的状态改为“终止中”。

[para:sync]
[:en] [`finish] synchronizes with the [*pop-front] operation that returns [`nullptr].
[:zh_CN] [`finish] 同步于返回 [`nullptr] 的 [*pop-front] 操作。
[div:end]
